Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.13,0:00:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[ARES] My heart raced the first\Ntime I laid eyes on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.01,0:00:18.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A beacon of hope,\Nshining so effortlessly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.85,0:00:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,in this dark, dull world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:23.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How could no one else\Nbut me see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.31,0:00:25.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Who she truly was?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.57,0:00:30.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[ARES]\NThe Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.90,0:00:33.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The only Blessing besides\Nthe Sage I ever bow to.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.03,0:00:35.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I worshipped her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.70,0:00:38.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I had finally found\Nmy purpose in life:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.75,0:00:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,To serve the Hero,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.50,0:00:43.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,in accordance with\Nthe Almighty's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.33,0:00:47.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[ARES] I was born to\Nright the wrongs of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.34,0:00:50.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,this sinful world and\Nfight alongside her!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.42,0:00:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[BUI] The relic of the\Nfirst Hero lies just ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.38,0:00:54.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lead me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.64,0:00:57.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I will have Ruti\Nat my side again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.52,0:01:01.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ares is here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.56,0:01:05.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah. Not only that,\Nhe's after Ruti.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.19,0:01:06.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The spirit drake.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.48,0:01:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He probably summoned\Nthat creature to get here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.94,0:01:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Back in the corridor, the plague\Neyes were his doing, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.28,0:01:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ares has proceeded\Nto the lower level.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.20,0:01:19.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And he's not alone,\Nthere's someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.62,0:01:21.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Can you tell who it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.37,0:01:24.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I can't. Whoever it is\Nworking alongside Ares
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.96,0:01:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,conceals their\Npresence with magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.00,0:01:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Is it Shisandan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.50,0:01:30.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The only one it could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.13,0:01:34.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But, what are they\Nplanning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.26,0:01:36.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No point in standing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.47,0:01:38.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If Shisandan is deceiving Ares,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.85,0:01:40.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,then we'll just have to\Nfind out why.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.02,0:01:41.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[RIT]\NRight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.85,0:01:43.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wait, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.39,0:01:46.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm lost, what exactly are the\Nfour of you going on about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.73,0:01:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sorry, but there's no time\Nto explain. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.57,0:01:56.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[gasps] Go where exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.12,0:02:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I am staying right here!\NWait, don't leave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.12,0:02:08.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[DANAN]\NI'm going ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.50,0:02:12.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[THEODORA] Danan! I brought you\Nalong for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.05,0:02:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No matter how things\Nturn out from here on,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.26,0:02:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I wanted us to face it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.30,0:02:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So I'd prefer if you didn't\Ncharge on ahead without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.22,0:02:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.35,0:02:25.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You truly are all brawn\Nand no brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.35,0:02:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You stick to your\Nfighting thing as usual
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.19,0:02:30.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,and I'll be the wits\Nof the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.69,0:02:34.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ah, not sure I follow,\Nbut all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.19,0:02:35.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You do things your way,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.28,0:02:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,and I'll do things mine,\Nthat sound good?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.16,0:02:44.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[DANAN grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.48,0:03:10.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[DANAN grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.77,0:03:11.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[ARES gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.91,0:03:21.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,D-Danan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:23.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, fancy seeing you alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.41,0:03:28.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ares. If you know what's good\Nfor you, stay out of my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.00,0:03:31.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[BUI] For a brute, that strike\Nwas impressively calculated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:33.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I can't even move my fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.92,0:03:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,However, he's still one-handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.06,0:03:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[DANAN] I almost forgot... and\Ndon't take this the wrong way,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.65,0:03:51.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm still gonna kick your ass\Nwhere you stand,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.77,0:03:53.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,but I oughta thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.94,0:03:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The loss of my right hand\Nmade me realize
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.07,0:03:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,just how worthless and weak\Nmy left hand had become.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.49,0:04:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Now, it's as strong\Nas my right hand was.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.95,0:04:08.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dragontail Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.42,0:04:16.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.92,0:04:19.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[BUI]\NAres! Help me! Ares!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.97,0:04:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[gasps] Me? Against a martial\Nartist like Danan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.30,0:04:26.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Seriously? I would not\Nstand a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.85,0:04:28.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[BUI]\NAres!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.22,0:04:29.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[ARES]\NNo, I have to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.93,0:04:32.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,There must be something\NI can do, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.23,0:04:33.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.44,0:04:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I always make the right\Nchoice when it counts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.23,0:04:39.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[ARES]\NAfter all, I'm the Sage!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.36,0:04:41.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gargantuan Storm Javelin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.54,0:04:48.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Go to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.49,0:04:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[DANAN groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.63,0:05:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You've been wounded by\Na blast through the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,and yet you stand\Nready for more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Even I've never observed a\Nmartial artist such as yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.47,0:05:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Your strength surpasses the role\Nallotted by your Blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:26.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[SHISANDAN grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.96,0:05:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're not the only\Nskilled fighter here, brute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.46,0:05:41.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Though my martial arts style is
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.80,0:05:44.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,often mistaken for\Nmere acrobatics.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.76,0:05:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well what d'ya know.\NIt looks like you got me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.23,0:06:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[ARES]\NAm I really all right with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.53,0:06:04.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes, of course I am, what's one\Nmore eliminated comrade?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.41,0:06:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[ARES] I, more than anyone,\Nknew how formidable Gideon was.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.49,0:06:15.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[ARES] And that's why I had\Nno choice but to get rid of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:18.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I couldn't be the Sage I was\Nmeant to with him in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.79,0:06:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[SHISANDAN]\NSage, I'm in your debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.92,0:06:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, spare me, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:24.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.72,0:06:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Be on your guard for traps here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.49,0:06:55.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[SHISANDAN]\NWe should have access now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.87,0:06:58.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How did you unlock\Nthis contraption?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.63,0:07:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Its origins date all the way\Nback to an extinct civilization.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.57,0:07:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[ARES]\NThe Holy Demon Slayer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:34.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Only one should be in existence!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.87,0:07:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So why are there more?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.50,0:07:37.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.79,0:07:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,None of these blades\Nis the Holy Demon Slayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.50,0:07:40.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[ARES gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.75,0:07:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[SHISANDAN] The sword\Nthe current Hero yields,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.29,0:07:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,what you call\Nthe Holy Demon Slayer,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.21,0:07:46.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,is a replica of\Nthe swords before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.72,0:07:48.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The blades bestowed\Nby the Almighty
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.67,0:07:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,and wielded by the first Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.55,0:07:52.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[ARES]\NThe true holy swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.64,0:07:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[SHISANDAN]\NAptly named, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.14,0:07:56.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,They will be known as\Nthe True Avengers,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.52,0:07:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,no, the Sacred Avengers,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.52,0:08:01.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,to distinguish them\Nfrom the replica.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.15,0:08:05.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[SHISANDAN]\NLike the sword she carries,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:08.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,the Hero, too, is but a copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.32,0:08:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The soul of the first Hero,\Nreplicated by the Almighty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.28,0:08:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A replicated soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.62,0:08:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Returning Ruti\Nto the Hero's path
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,requires precisely two steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.16,0:08:22.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,First, you must pair the Hero\Nwith one of the Sacred Avengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.58,0:08:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,When wielded by her,\Nits power will
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.59,0:08:28.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,enhance the Hero's Blessing\Nand restore the innate impulses
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:30.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,that have been weakened\Nby the Devil's Blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.76,0:08:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Simple enough if it means\Nhaving Ruti back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.51,0:08:35.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The next step is most difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.89,0:08:37.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Whatever it takes, I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.89,0:08:39.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You must strike him\Nfrom her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.73,0:08:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Her brother is the reason\Nshe's strayed from her path
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.10,0:08:44.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,and wishes to live\Nan ordinary life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.32,0:08:48.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What's so difficult about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:00.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.84,0:09:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.10,0:09:18.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stay on guard, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Here, Big Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.32,0:09:29.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thunderwaker!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.19,0:09:30.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So, you kept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.74,0:09:33.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[RUTI]\NYes, it's yours, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.24,0:09:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.58,0:09:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My dearest disciple.\NWhat a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.76,0:09:56.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.64,0:09:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Paralyzing Flame!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.56,0:10:03.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Just die already, Gideon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.98,0:10:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[RED]\NAres!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.52,0:10:10.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sacred Magic Shield, rise!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.45,0:10:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ares, there's still time.\NSurrender now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.45,0:10:23.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll surrender once you're\Nat my side again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.75,0:10:27.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gargantuan Storm Javelin!\NMost Sacred Punisher!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.35,0:10:43.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Get me the hell outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.06,0:10:49.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[roars]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You mustn't be so quick\Nto go running off like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.07,0:10:54.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stay within sight\Nfor now, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.44,0:10:55.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.99,0:11:03.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[ALBERT]\NAre you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.45,0:11:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[DANAN]\NWhat, this? It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:11.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't be absurd, it's fatal.\NDrink this, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:21.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[ARES]\NRuti need only wield this sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.93,0:11:29.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Martial Art. Great Whirlwind!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.31,0:11:31.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.02,0:11:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[SPIRIT DRAKE 12A roars]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.84,0:11:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[SHISANDAN]\NSo, her power already exceeds
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.21,0:11:56.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,that of the former Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:11:58.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Something's coming below!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.80,0:12:00.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.22,0:12:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Move, Rit! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.43,0:12:10.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[THEODORA]\NHoly Chains!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.15,0:12:12.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Theodora?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.07,0:12:16.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.70,0:12:23.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.57,0:12:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Curse me if you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.70,0:12:27.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll atone with my life after.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.00,0:12:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But your life must be sacrificed\Nto preserve this world's peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.58,0:12:34.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And why my life?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.96,0:12:36.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Because you are the Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.84,0:12:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I never wanted to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.34,0:12:41.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Not once have I ever\Nasked for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.18,0:12:45.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,There's plenty out there who\Ndesire and earn that title.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.47,0:12:47.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So, why give it to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.98,0:12:57.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Countless lives will be lost\Nin the name of your ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.61,0:12:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Faceless lives you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.74,0:13:03.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why must I sacrifice\Nmy own life to save strangers?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.24,0:13:05.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Because it is the\NAlmighty's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.24,0:13:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.16,0:13:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[RED]\NRit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.25,0:13:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[laughs] A heart-\Nwrenching dilemma:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.29,0:13:15.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Will you save your beloved\Nor dear sister? Your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.63,0:13:19.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[THEODORA]\NFace the facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.42,0:13:22.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gideon may wield a sword\Nbetter than anyone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.59,0:13:25.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,but he can't save those\Ndear to him without your aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.80,0:13:28.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Humanity needs you\Nto be the Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.19,0:13:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[RIT]\NThat's nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.53,0:13:43.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't place my life\Nin her hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.24,0:13:44.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You don't have the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.07,0:13:46.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.49,0:13:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Was it not the Hero\Nwho saved your kingdom?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.29,0:13:51.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,As living proof, you should\Nknow more than anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.70,0:13:53.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,that the world needs the Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.04,0:13:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.58,0:13:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[THEODORA]\NHow am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.08,0:14:00.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[RIT] It wasn't simply the Hero,\Nthe Guide, or the Crusader
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.26,0:14:02.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,that saved me and my country.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.59,0:14:05.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The ones I have to thank\Nfor that, for saving us,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.68,0:14:09.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,are Ruti, Red, and you yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.35,0:14:10.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.97,0:14:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.39,0:14:15.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The Hero is much more\Nthan a Blessing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.77,0:14:18.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She's a person,\Nwho has the Blessing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.82,0:14:22.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[RIT] It took much more than\Nthe Hero to save Loggervia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.99,0:14:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My country is here today because
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.61,0:14:26.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,you three inspired us\Nto rise up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.62,0:14:28.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You made us fight for ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.08,0:14:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The will of the Almighty\Nis what I preserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.50,0:14:36.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Without question.\NI will not rebel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.46,0:14:38.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If His will involves placing\Nthe fate of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.50,0:14:40.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,on unwilling shoulders,\Nthen I'll show Him
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.38,0:14:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,just how wrong He is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.67,0:14:42.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's just wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.05,0:14:45.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,and I don't care whether\NHe's an almighty god or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.42,0:14:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[THEODORA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.34,0:14:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[SHISANDAN]\NIt seems we agree on one thing:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.55,0:14:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The Hero does not simply exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.64,0:14:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Only those who strive to be the\NHero are worthy of that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.93,0:14:57.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And yet the Almighty is\Ntoo foolish to understand
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.27,0:14:59.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,a simple fact that\Nyou all grasp easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.81,0:15:01.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.28,0:15:02.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.99,0:15:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, Rit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.32,0:15:11.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rise, Iron Wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.79,0:15:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This is the end, Gideon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.21,0:15:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, Gideon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.85,0:15:33.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[RUTI screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.39,0:15:39.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A measly replica\Nmanaging to shatter
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.40,0:15:42.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,the Sacred Avenger is\Na most impressive feat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.87,0:15:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[ARES chuckling]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.08,0:15:58.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Poof! Gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.96,0:16:01.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The Guide and his little\Nbeloved are both gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.79,0:16:03.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm better!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:05.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're dead, yet I still live!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.21,0:16:08.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Victor and vanquished!\NThe Sage and the foolish one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[ARES cackling]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tornado Cutter!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.93,0:16:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[TISSE screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.69,0:16:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[ARES]\NYou conniving little assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.98,0:16:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.69,0:16:30.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How could you ever\Nbetray your own party?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.36,0:16:32.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My loyalty is to Ruti only.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.91,0:16:35.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And it's the Hero's\Nduty to sacrifice all
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.41,0:16:37.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,in the name of her Blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.37,0:16:40.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That sacrifice is for\Nthe Hero's greater good,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.41,0:16:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,for her own happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.92,0:16:47.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How would you know\Nanything about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.80,0:16:50.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's true, my lady is\Nformidable in a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.47,0:16:52.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Even when home, she's shy\Nand can't read the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.01,0:16:54.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But her heart's full of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.89,0:16:57.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She's just as normal and\Nordinary as everyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.97,0:17:00.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I won't let you take\Nmy precious friend when you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.31,0:17:03.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,can't even understand\Nthat simple fact about her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.02,0:17:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[cackling]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.08,0:17:18.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.95,0:17:20.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[GODWIN yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.04,0:17:22.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Forget about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.30,0:17:28.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm not teaming up\Nwith these fools,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.17,0:17:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I just hate looking at\Ncocky bastards like you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.38,0:17:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,who act all high\Nand mighty because
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.76,0:17:33.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,they don't know\Nthey're the bad guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.01,0:17:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The hell do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.31,0:17:38.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What are you driveling on about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.81,0:17:44.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.15,0:17:47.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,As if a paltry little spider\Ncould outwit a Sage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.99,0:18:01.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[DADAN] I won't act like\NI follow what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.41,0:18:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Or what the Hero\Nis going through.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.92,0:18:08.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[DANAN] What is right,\Nand what is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.34,0:18:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But, there's one thing\Neven I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.96,0:18:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gideon! Rit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.59,0:18:16.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The two of you are my comrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.97,0:18:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll get you out of this mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.64,0:18:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're not dying on my watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.97,0:18:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No one's gonna\Ntell me otherwise!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.27,0:18:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Martial Art:\NRising Dragon's Roar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.12,0:18:46.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.29,0:18:48.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why won't you just die already?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.38,0:18:51.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You and your worthless Blessing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.21,0:18:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ares!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.01,0:18:57.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Die, Gideon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.47,0:18:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Go, Red!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.43,0:19:05.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[RIT screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.02,0:19:09.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Now the killing blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.94,0:19:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.57,0:19:16.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate\NMr. Crawly Waly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.70,0:19:19.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You should see the look on your\Nface now, you uppity bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.08,0:19:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How did that\Nstupid spider get me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.13,0:19:37.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[ARES]\NHelp me, Shisandan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:39.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Heal me, bring me my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.72,0:19:43.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Somebody. Anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.89,0:19:47.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[ARES]\NHow can this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.56,0:19:49.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why is it always you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.02,0:19:53.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm more powerful! Far wiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:19:58.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ruti. O My Lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.61,0:20:03.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It was foretold, that I was born\Nto serve only the Hero, and yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.46,0:20:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I want to live my own peaceful\Nlife alongside my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Regardless, you are\Nstill a threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.34,0:20:21.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,In the name of the Asura,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.47,0:20:24.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I will end your life\Nonce and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.46,0:20:53.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Is me living my own life\Nreally so wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.25,0:20:54.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.55,0:20:57.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You must fulfill your duty\Nas the world's Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.38,0:20:59.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The Almighty and\Nall humanity won't allow
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.76,0:21:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,the Hero to lead\Na peaceful life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.14,0:21:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Something's burning in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.31,0:21:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The fire of rage!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.56,0:21:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[SHISANDAN]\NSuch power!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.27,0:21:16.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Even if the Devil's\NBlessing sparked this,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.23,0:21:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I can't believe it\Nmanifested so clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.74,0:21:22.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.24,0:21:27.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The life my brother\Nand I shared! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.29,0:21:31.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[RUTI yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.75,0:21:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.59,0:21:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[grunts] This time\NI will finish you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.97,0:21:44.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[RUTI yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.26,0:21:46.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[SHISANDAN] At last!\NShe wields the Sacred Avengers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.60,0:21:50.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,In the end, I was\Nat least able to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.58,0:22:08.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[RED]\NShe'll heal fine with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.33,0:22:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why are you saving her?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.54,0:22:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[RED]\NBecause she's my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.08,0:22:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How'd I get mixed up\Nwith a bunch of do-gooders?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.09,0:22:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[RED]\NIt's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.96,0:22:21.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I mean, yeah,\NTheodora turned against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.42,0:22:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[RED]\NAnd, yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.93,0:22:25.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Even though she\Nbecame our enemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.89,0:22:28.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,the last thing I want\Nfor my sister
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.39,0:22:30.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,is to lose a comrade\Nbecause of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.52,0:22:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ruti! I was getting worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.32,0:22:48.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.20,0:22:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.34,0:23:04.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tisse!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.92,0:23:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Please come to your\Nsenses, my Lady Ruti.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.43,0:23:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The man standing before you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.64,0:23:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,is someone very\Nprecious in your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.69,0:23:18.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Please do not harm him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.27,0:23:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Please, don't.
